---
import Navbar from '../components/Navbar.astro';
import Banner from '../components/Banner.astro';
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

import TeamBanner from '../components/TeamBanner.astro';
import ContactForm from '../components/ContactForm.astro';
import Services from '../components/Services.astro';

// Welcome to Astro! Wondering what to do next? Check out the Astro documentation at https://docs.astro.build
// Don't want to use any of this? Delete everything in this file, the `assets`, `components`, and `layouts` directories, and start fresh.
---

<Layout title="Abogados - Type Of Legal">
	<Navbar/>
	<main>
		<Banner />
		<Services />
		<section id="about" class="about">

			<div class="about-wrapper">
				<div class="bg-image"></div>
				<div class="content-overlay">
					<div class="content-wrapper">
						<div class="content">
							<h2>Derecho hecho simple</h2>
							<p>Type of Legal nace del deseo de hacer derecho de otro modo. Creemos en el asesoramiento jurídico como una herramienta clave e indispensable a la hora de gestionar y hacer crecer tu negocio especialmente en un entorno como el actual: digital, complejo y en continua transformación.</p>
							<p>Entendemos que un asesoramiento jurídico eficaz y de calidad no tiene porqué implicar un lenguaje complejo y unas tarifas desorbitadas.</p>
							<p>Si tienes un negocio con presencia en el entorno digital estamos seguros de que podemos ayudarte.</p>
						</div>
			
					</div>
					
				</div>
			
			</div>
			<TeamBanner />

		</section>
		<section id="contact" class="contact">
			<div class="contact-header">
				<h2>¿Necesitas asesoramiento legal especializado?</h2>
				<p>Nuestro equipo de abogados está listo para ayudarte con cualquier consulta legal relacionada con tecnología y derecho digital.</p>
			</div>

			<ContactForm/>
		</section>
	</main>
	
</Layout>
<style is:global>

@keyframes appear {
        from {
            opacity: 0.1;
            scale: 0.8;
        }
        to {
            opacity: 1;
            scale: 1;
        }

    }
	html {
  scroll-behavior: smooth;
}
	  :root {
    --background: 0 0% 100%;
    --foreground: 220 10% 3.9%;
    --card: 0 0% 100%;
    --card-foreground: 220 10% 3.9%;
    --popover: 0 0% 100%;
    --popover-foreground: 220 10% 3.9%;
    --primary: 142 34% 42%;
    --primary-foreground: 355.7 100% 97.3%;
    --secondary: 140 15% 95%;
    --secondary-foreground: 220 10% 3.9%;
    --muted: 140 15% 95%;
    --muted-foreground: 220 5% 40%;
    --accent: 140 15% 95%;
    --accent-foreground: 220 10% 3.9%;
    --destructive: 0 84.2% 60.2%;
    --destructive-foreground: 0 0% 98%;
    --border: 125 15% 92%;
    --input: 125 15% 92%;
    --ring: 142 34% 42%;
    --radius: 0.5rem;
  }
* {
	font-family: sans-serif;
	overflow: visible !important;

}

main{
	margin-top: 95px;
}



h2{
				margin: 0;
				font-size: 40px;
				font-weight: bold;
				color: #2e3c2e;
			}

#about{
	background: #f0f5f0de;
	display: flex;
	flex-direction: column;
	align-items: center;



	.about-wrapper{
		width: 100%;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
		position: relative;
		.bg-image{
            position: absolute;
            content: "";
            height: 100%;
            width: 100%;
              /* Fondo degradado base: de #f0f5f0 a white */

  /* Imagen encima */
  background-image: url('/src/assets/images/lorene-farrugia-JpmC-tAHiVA-unsplash.jpg');
  background-position: right center;
  background-size: cover;
  background-repeat: no-repeat;
  background-blend-mode: normal;

  /* Difuminado de la imagen hacia la izquierda */
  mask-image: linear-gradient(to left, black 10%, transparent 50%);
  -webkit-mask-image: linear-gradient(to left, black 10%, transparent 50%);
        }

		.content-overlay{
            padding: 100px 0px;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #f0f5f0de, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.589));
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;

            .content-wrapper{
                display: flex;
                align-items: center;
                position: relative;
                width: 100%;
                padding: 0px 20px;
                max-width: 1300px;
                box-sizing: border-box;

                .content{
                    display: flex;
                    flex-direction: column;
                    justify-content: center;
                    max-width: 45%;
                    padding: 20px;
                    gap: 15px;
					animation: appear linear;
        animation-timeline: view();
        animation-range: entry 0;

                    h1{
                        font-size: 60px;
                        margin: 0;
                    }

                    p{
                        font-weight: bold;
                        color: #5a6b5a;
                        font-size: 20px;
                    }
                    .banner-buttons{
                        display: flex;
                        align-items: center;
                        gap: 20px;

                        button{
                        border-radius: 0.5rem;
                        text-decoration: none;
                        color: #2e3c2e;
                        padding: 12px 22px;
                        text-align: center;
                        vertical-align: text-bottom;
                        font-weight: 600;
                        transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out;
                        outline: none;
                        border: 0;
                        cursor: pointer;
                        }

                        .style1{
                            background-color: #4d8b6c;
                            color: white;

                            
                         }

                        .style1:hover{
                            background-color: #3d6e55;
                            color: white;
                        }

                        .style2{
                            border: 1px solid #4d8b6c;
                            background-color: white;
                            color: #4d8b6c;
                        }

                        .style2:hover{
                            background-color: #d5e3db
                        }
                    }
                }
            }

            h1{
            animation: slide-up 1s ease-out;
            font-size: 2.25rem;        /* text-4xl */
            font-weight: 700;          /* font-bold */
            letter-spacing: -0.015em;  /* tracking-tight */
            color: #2e3c2e;
            }
        }

		.about-content{
			position: absolute;
			z-index: 1000px;
		}

		h2{
			width: 100%;
			margin-bottom: 40px;
		}
		
		p{
			margin: 0;
				font-size: 20px;
				color: #5a6b5a;
				font-weight: bold;
			margin-bottom: 10px;
		}
	}
}

#contact{
	display: flex;
	justify-content: center;
	flex-direction: column;
	padding-top: 30px;
	align-items: center;
	background-image: url('/src/assets/images/pexels---4059426.jpg');
	scroll-margin-top: 90px; 

	.contact-header{
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 10px;
		animation: appear linear;
        animation-timeline: view();
        animation-range: entry 0;
	}
	p{
			margin: 0;
				font-size: 20px;
				color: white;
				font-weight: bold;
			margin-bottom: 10px;
			text-align: center;
		}

	h2{
		margin-top: 50px;
		color: white;
		text-align: center;

	}
}

    /* Media Queries */
    @media (max-width: 1400px) {
    #about .bg-image{
        mask-image: linear-gradient(to left, black 20%, transparent 45%);
        -webkit-mask-image: linear-gradient(to left, black 20%, transparent 45%);
    }

}

    @media (max-width: 1300px) {
		.contact-header{
			padding: 0px 30px !important;
		}
    }

    @media (max-width: 900px) {
        #about .about-wrapper .bg-image{
            mask-image: linear-gradient(to left, black 0%, transparent 60%);
            -webkit-mask-image: linear-gradient(to left, black 0% transparent 60%);
        }

        #about .about-wrapper .content-overlay .content-wrapper .content{
            max-width: 60%;
        }
    }



    @media (max-width: 770px) {
        #about .about-wrapper .bg-image{
            mask-image: linear-gradient(to left, black -400px, transparent 40%);
            -webkit-mask-image: linear-gradient(to left, black -400px, transparent 40%);
        }

        #about .about-wrapper .content-overlay .content-wrapper .content{
            max-width: 100%;
        }

        .banner-buttons{
            flex-direction: column;
            button{
                width: 100%;
            }
        }

    }

    @media (max-width: 500px) {
        #about .about-wrapper .bg-image{
            mask-image: linear-gradient(to left, black -400px, transparent 40%);
            -webkit-mask-image: linear-gradient(to left, black -400px, transparent 40%);
        }

        #about .about-wrapper .content-overlay .content-wrapper .content{
            max-width: 100%;
        }

  

      
    }

@media (max-width: 700px) {
	h2{
            text-align: center !important;
        }
}
</style>